{"tid":85230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉德華泰國拍廣告墮馬傳腰脊骨裂 乘醫療專機返港","createTime":"2017-01-18T07:26:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-18T14:18:26.000Z","uid":65346,"like":52,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"94e94bcf1572a7e23e84c6bd26f0e4dfd62a3555","tid":85230,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T07:26:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170118/56187908\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170118%2F56187908&d=6Vf6nd7MzY2gffjjA7L720sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=98f5a52d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170118%2F56187908&h=f4bc945d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170118/56187908</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n刀仔 ~~<br />\n<br />\n55歲劉德華自2000年開始做道地代言人，劉德華本周一已出發前往泰國拍新廣告，據當地可靠消息，華仔往泰國郊區拍攝一場騎馬嘅場面，馬匹忽然發狂，華仔不慎墮馬，馬匹更踩到華仔腰脊，令他腰脊骨裂，而廣告亦要暫停拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n華仔立刻被送去泰國一間醫院治療，因為腰脊受傷，行動不便，必須坐醫療專機回港，再接受香港醫生診治。《蘋果》今日聯絡劉德華，不過暫時未有回應。<br />\n當地一位知情製作人龍哥指，知道華仔昨日在距離曼谷三小時車程的寇立開工，當時有數匹馬在場，華仔所騎的馬忽然失控，將華仔拋下，被馬蹄踩到脊椎，據知傷勢頗嚴重。"},{"pid":"90d1a55199a133254214771adfc2082ce614300e","tid":85230,"uid":48834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T07:31:20.000Z","msg":"人善天不欺"},{"pid":"38eaf3ac277e556be113790c879c34ddfba4ca20","tid":85230,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T07:32:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02d7adfdb95bbf86b20e3b2795182f14fd0d97a8","tid":85230,"uid":1441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T07:34:23.000Z","msg":"民間特首墮馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 